<section
    id="positive-specialization"
    class="relative text-[#e7e5e4] font-serif min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-12 md:py-24 border-b border-emerald-900/10"
>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <span
                class="text-emerald-500/80 text-xs md:text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase block mb-4"
                >VII. El Genio</span
            >
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#e7e5e4] mb-6">
                El Nacimiento del Genio
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-[#a8a29e] max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                En una tribu de cazadores, todos cazan. En una ciudad de trigo, uno cultiva y nueve
                pueden soñar.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <!-- Card 1 -->
            <div
                class="bg-[#1c1917] p-8 rounded border border-emerald-900/10 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-colors group"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-900/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-emerald-900/40 text-emerald-500"
                >
                    <!-- Icon: Pot/Craft -->
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke-width="1.5"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        class="w-6 h-6"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M14.25 7.756a4.5 4.5 0 100 8.488M7.5 10.5h5.25m-5.25 3h5.25M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#e7e5e4] mb-3">El Artesano</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-[#a8a29e]">
                    Liberado de la búsqueda de comida, las manos pudieron perfeccionar la arcilla,
                    el metal y la tela.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 2 -->
            <div
                class="bg-[#1c1917] p-8 rounded border border-emerald-900/10 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-colors group"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-900/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-emerald-900/40 text-emerald-500"
                >
                    <!-- Icon: Health/Plus -->
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke-width="1.5"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        class="w-6 h-6"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M12 4.5v15m7.5-7.5h-15"></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#e7e5e4] mb-3">El Sanador</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-[#a8a29e]">
                    El tiempo libre permitió la observación. Entendimos las plantas no solo como
                    comida, sino como medicina.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 3 -->
            <div
                class="bg-[#1c1917] p-8 rounded border border-emerald-900/10 hover:border-emerald-500/30 transition-colors group"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-900/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 group-hover:bg-emerald-900/40 text-emerald-500"
                >
                    <!-- Icon: Star/Scope -->
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke-width="1.5"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                        class="w-6 h-6"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            d="M11.48 3.499a.562.562 0 011.04 0l2.125 5.111a.563.563 0 00.475.345l5.518.442c.499.04.701.663.321.988l-4.204 3.602a.563.563 0 00-.182.557l1.285 5.385a.562.562 0 01-.84.61l-4.725-2.885a.563.563 0 00-.586 0L6.982 20.54a.562.562 0 01-.84-.61l1.285-5.386a.562.562 0 00-.182-.557l-4.204-3.602a.563.563 0 01.321-.988l5.518-.442a.563.563 0 00.475-.345L11.48 3.5z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#e7e5e4] mb-3">El Astrónomo</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-[#a8a29e]">
                    Necesitábamos predecir las cosechas. Así que miramos arriba y mapeamos las
                    estrellas. Inventamos el calendario.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
